===Noun===
'''trousers''' {{pluralonly}}

# {{UK|Canada}} An [[article]] of [[clothing]] that covers the part of the body between the [[waist]] and the [[ankle]]s, and is [[divide]]d into a separate part for each [[leg]].

====Synonyms====
* [[pants]] (Australia, Canada, US); [[strides]] (Australia)

====Hyponyms====
* [[jeans]]
* [[pantaloons]]
* [[shorts]]
* [[slacks]]
